name: The Backrooms Level <UNDEFINED>
description: This game is based of of The Backrooms, there are obviously many different variations of the backrooms but I tried to keep this one as canon (Not A-sync lore) as possible. There is a lot missing or things that are not yet added, but the key features like items movement and general vibes are there. This game is only in its early alphas so its nothing big at the moment, if you have any suggestions i will be glad to read them in the description.
